  sodium: 1130 mg
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chicken-and-creamy-italian-white-beans-66a12556bbd88d3e9c686ca8
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Southern Europe
